    "extract": "Speed Stick is an American brand of deodorant/antiperspirant produced by multinational healthcare company Colgate-Palmolive. It was formerly known as \"Mennen Speed Stick\" prior to Colgate-Palmolive's purchase of The Mennen Company. Currently, the products feature the words \"by Mennen\" in a small font on the label. Speed Stick comes in both deodorant and antiperspirant forms. Speed Stick is both a sponsor and the official antiperspirant of the NHL."
